14 hours ago, tonimark said:

got stuck at end of loading 

Most commonly caused by an incompatible mod or a mod conflict. Try to isolate the mod causing this: remove half of your mods, see if KSP loads. Yes: re-add half of the removed mods, try again. No: remove half of the remaining mods. 

Repeat until you find the mod causing the issue.

I'm wondering though, in your mod list I see two lines for Kerbalism?
